room_title: Escape room "The Doll Factory" by Escape Hour in Wabash
room_description: Many years ago a young girl, Sally, and her father lived inside a doll factory her father owned.   Sally often played with a strange doll and named it “Miss Kitty”.   Sally’s father felt that an evil entity had possessed the doll. One day tragedy stuck the factory when a fire started in the facility and Sally died. Thomas blames the entity for killing his daughter.  He wants the doll found and destroyed.   Can you find the doll and escape the building?
